OL,3,CSon of couple murdered in their own
OL,4,Chome pays tribute to 'perfect parents'
OL,6,FThe son of a couple who were murdered
OL,7,Fin their own home in Newhaven says
OL,8,Fthey were the 'perfect parents'.
OL,10,FChloe and Joshua Bashford were
OL,11,Fbrutally killed by Chloe's stepfather
OL,12,FDerek Martin on 9 June 2023.
OL,14,FThe 67-year old entered the Bashford's
OL,15,Fhome and struck Chloe with a hammer
OL,16,Fbefore strangling her. When Joshua
OL,17,Freturned from work half an hour later,
OL,18,FMartin stabbed and then strangled him.
