OL,6,FToday after Martin was found guilty of
OL,7,Fmurder by a jury at Brighton Crown
OL,8,FCourt, one of the Bashford's four
OL,9,Fchildren, Brooklyn, gave his reaction
OL,10,Fto the conviction.
OL,12,F"I think everyone's happy with it
OL,13,Freally, because it's what it's
OL,14,Fdeserved," Brooklyn said.
OL,16,F"I think everyone's a bit emotional.
OL,17,FIt's been two and a half years, it's
OL,18,Ftaken quite a long time to finally get
OL,19,Fhere, when realistically it should
OL,20,Fhave been done a while ago.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
