OL,6,F"But everyone's happy with it, it's
OL,7,Fwhat it deserves, it's what it is.
OL,9,FSpeaking about his parents Brooklyn
OL,10,Fsaid: "They were amazing people
OL,11,Freally, perfect parents, just the best
OL,12,Fparents you could ask for really.
OL,14,F"It's hard to find the right words for
OL,15,Fit, they were just perfect parents,
OL,16,Fgood people.(3:00) Always there for us
OL,17,Fand we'll always remember them.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
