OL,3,CSon of couple murdered in their own
OL,4,Chome pays tribute to 'perfect parents'
OL,6,F"Everyone's had to adapt to a whole
OL,7,Fnew life. I think since it's happened,
OL,8,Fit just feels like two separate lives
OL,9,Fwith that.
OL,11,F"It's really hard to grasp a new life
OL,12,Freally, but everyone's coping,
OL,13,Feveryone's managing to do it, which is
OL,14,Fgood, and over time, we're just going
OL,15,Fto have to learn to live with it."
OL,17,FJoshua's brother Billy Bashford said
OL,18,Fthe family is pleased with the
OL,19,Fconviction and feels they have justice
OL,20,Ffor Joshua and Chloe.
