OL,6,F"I think the family's been dragged
OL,7,Fthrough it quite a lot, but I think
OL,8,Fit's just a bit of a surreal
OL,9,Fexperience really.
OL,11,F"The fact that we've all got to this
OL,12,Fpoint and we've got the right result,
OL,13,Fwe all wanted.
OL,15,F"More importantly, obviously justice
OL,16,Ffor Josh and Chloe.
OL,18,FSpeaking about the couple, he added:
OL,19,F"They loved each other so much, you
OL,20,Fcould clearly see that.
