OL,6,F"They were such a happy, happy family.
OL,8,F"And I think it was such a shock to
OL,9,Fall of us that it came out of the
OL,10,Fblue, but they were both such loving
OL,11,Fparents."
OL,13,F"Everyone knew Josh and Chloe just as
OL,14,Fa bit of a ray of sunshine really.
OL,16,F"For my family, for Chloe's family, we
OL,17,Fall just miss them so, so much.
OL,19,F"It's been a horrible last couple of
OL,20,Fyears and they're going to be sorely
OL,21,Fmissed.
