OL,6,F"The fact we're standing here today
OL,7,Fstill without them, I think it's
OL,8,Fstarting to sink in properly now.
OL,10,F"Josh was like a best mate to me, and
OL,11,Fmy sister left a massive hole in our
OL,12,Fheart and I can't describe how much I
OL,13,Fmiss them every day."
